	<title>
		<paragraph x="12" y="+4" width="605" height="0" style="headline" tabs="0" indent="0"><![CDATA[<B><TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="12" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">Speculation</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT></B>]]></paragraph>
	</title>
	<body>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+16" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">You may be asked to speculate on future developments. What is important here is not to have a prepared answer, but to have phrases to help you speculate. Here are some phrases to use when speculating on future developments:</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">- Maybe </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">- Perhaps</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">- I hope</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">- It would be good if......</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">- We can't tell</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="_sans" SIZE="12" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0"> </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#0000FF" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0"><B>Strategies</B></FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="_sans" SIZE="12" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0"> </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="25" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">1.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="35" y="=" width="400" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">Practise speculating on your own when, for example, you listen to the news. What might happen? How much can you foretell? What are the various possibilities?</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="400" height="0" style="normal" tabs="25" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">2.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="35" y="=" width="400" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">Practise comparing different versions of the news, or different aspects of your life. Get used to the phrases we use for these functions.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
